SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 46
A bill to amend 1976 PA 399, entitled
"Safe drinking water act,"
by amending sections 2, 3, and 15 (MCL 325.1002, 325.1003, and
325.1015), section 2 as amended by 1998 PA 56 and section 15 as
amended by 1993 PA 165.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
